---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Virtual Tour | ISJ Jakarta"
  description="Explore The Independent School of Jakarta campus from anywhere in the world. Walk through classrooms, the swimming pool, football pitch, and outdoor learning spaces in Pondok Indah."
  canonicalUrl="/admissions/virtual-tour"
>

  <!-- Introduction -->
  <section class="pt-[var(--space-section)] px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[var(--content-narrow)]">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="label mb-5">Admissions</p>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-[length:var(--text-2xl)] md:text-[length:var(--text-3xl)] font-light text-navy leading-[1.1] mb-8">Virtual Tour</h1>
        <p class="text-[length:var(--text-base)] leading-relaxed text-charcoal-light">
          Walk through the ISJ campus in Pondok Indah from anywhere in the world. Explore the classrooms, sports facilities, swimming pool, and outdoor learning spaces.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 360 Embed -->
  <section class="section-pad px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[var(--content-wide)]">
      <div class="reveal">
        <div class="w-full aspect-[16/9] overflow-hidden rounded-sm">
          <iframe
            src="https://360vpro.id/isj_v2/"
            title="ISJ Campus Virtual Tour"
            class="w-full h-full border-0"
            loading="lazy"
            allowfullscreen
          ></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Visit in person -->
  <section class="px-6 pb-[var(--space-section)]">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[var(--content-narrow)]">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="text-[length:var(--text-base)] leading-relaxed text-charcoal-light mb-6">
          A virtual tour is a useful starting point, but there is no substitute for visiting in person. ISJ runs open campus tours throughout the year. For a closer look at what the campus offers, see the <a href=/school-life/campus class="text-navy hover:text-navy/70 transition-colors underline underline-offset-2 decoration-charcoal/20">Campus &amp; Facilities</a> page.
        </p>
        <a href=/admissions/arrange-a-tour class="whisper-link">Arrange a tour</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
